text: Kori Kelley Seehafer (born 30 April 1975) is a road cyclist from United States. She represented her nation at the 2005 and 2008 UCI Road World Championships. ==References== ==External links== * profile at Procyclingstats.com Category:1975 births Category:American female cyclists Category:Living people Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
